Copy all *.h files to CodeBlocks\MinGW\include where u install it
Copy all *.a files to CodeBlocks\MinGW\lib
open CodeBloack
      open Settings\Compiler\Linker Settings
      Add CodeBlocks\MinGW\lib\libbgi.a file to  link libraries
      Copy below lines to Other link options
          -lbgi
          -lgdi32
          -lcomdlg32
          -luuid
          -loleaut32
          -lole32
#include<graphics.h> in your cpp file and use graphics ....
